MG_Mountain_Course_GK_v2

Improvements:
Only the first 4 levels, and last level, will now kill players when they fail.
Added 3 more levels (effectively doubling the size of the original map).
Removed the AFK killer, as any AFKs will be teleported to the end of the map upon completion anyway.
Made a few structural changes to improve FPS.
